            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained pasta</strong> to the pan with the<strong> pesto</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and give everything a good old mix up&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Cook for 1-2 min or until the sauce begins to stick to the pasta</p>\r\n<p>Tip: add a small splash of starchy pasta water if you want to loosen the sauce a little!</p>\r\n<p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper&nbsp;</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1060.-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1060.-step-7-x400.jpg",
